{"tid":682672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【畫風驚悚】小孩嚇到痙攣昏倒 日兒童繪本被逼下架","createTime":"2018-05-29T05:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T05:50:45.000Z","uid":75969,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f89adf885b084b3582ec8ac2f79a080394af9573","tid":682672,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180528/_2018052820105474573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180528%2F_2018052820105474573.jpg&h=85163570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有人在網上拍賣《蜘蛛丈夫與青蛙》。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n許多父母都會選擇兒童繪本作為學前兒童讀物，日本一本畫風「超驚悚」的兒童繪本，由於插畫與故事內容太驚嚇，讓兒童大哭不已，當局緊急回收這批出版僅7日的繪本。<br />\n<br />\n由松谷美代子所著繪本《蜘蛛丈夫與青蛙》於1969年發行，以5至8歲的兒童作為導向，故事情節改編自非洲民俗故事。然而，繪本故事內容與插畫太過可怕，許多兒童閱讀後嚇到不停大哭，甚至引發痙攣及昏倒的症狀，因此發行不到1周，就被緊急下架，禁止發行。<br />\n<br />\n《蜘蛛丈夫與青蛙》故事內容包含獵人蜘蛛將青蛙抓來吃、青蛙威脅蜘蛛吃掉心臟、還有青蛙威脅蜘蛛丈夫毆打蜘蛛太太等情節。書中的插畫風格帶血腥成份，配色也以黑、紅為主。由於該書內容以童話繪本的基準而言，實在太過殘忍，因此造成當時輿論反彈，要求下架回收。<br />\n<br />\n由於繪本發行當時不過7天就被緊急下架，因此市面已很難找到這繪本，但亦有人看準商機，在網上拍賣《蜘蛛丈夫與青蛙》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180528/_2018052820105645119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180528%2F_2018052820105645119.jpg&h=b86b4833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180528/_2018052820105672380.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180528%2F_2018052820105672380.jpg&h=51d7f20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180528/_2018052820105563455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180528%2F_2018052820105563455.jpg&h=ed45ff26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180528/_2018052820105512125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180528%2F_2018052820105512125.jpg&h=da1b6fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/726895\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F726895&d=MFJqdupFcKWnelv73%2FLeok%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c2176836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F726895&h=e3b6a311\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/726895</a>"},{"pid":"fabadc246776fcbc8082e2551837869ca0a7a4d1","tid":682672,"uid":36927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"其實我真係覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f5af143559e509bf9a047b5ab2a8192fbfbc9d","tid":682672,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fabadc246776fcbc8082e2551837869ca0a7a4d1","tid":682672,"uid":36927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"其實我真係覺得好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"想買本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be585b27a2c2d2700162eb2d895055cf1a91528f","tid":682672,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"痙攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cede30c7a1cd642e0da2a5ed65ee396e810eac17","tid":682672,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"近50年前嘅繪本故事內容，或變成某強國嘅現實事